        10t^2</m>, where <m>t</m> is in hours.
      </p>

      <task workspace="10%">
        <p>
          Write a definite integral for the distance the car travels during the first three hours.
        </p>
      </task>

      <task>
        <p>
          Sketch a graph of velocity against time and represent the distance
          traveled during the first three hours as an area on your graph.
        </p>

        <image>

